column2: SELECT TOP # ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY p.objid DESC) as RowNumber, p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.u BETWEEN # AND # AND g BETWEEN # AND #
